extends layout

block content
 body(style='background-color:#d1e0fa !important;')
  include _navbar
  div(class='jumbotron') 
   div(class='col-md-2')
   div(class='col-md-2')
    div(class='name') Digital Diary
   div(class='col-md-8 sideContent') 
    div(class='notes') Donâ€™t miss life moments. Record you life moments. We will help you
    a(class='btn loginBtn' href='/auth/dropbox') Login with Dropbox
    - if(error)
     div(class='text-danger') #{error}
  div(class='container homeContent') 
   div(class='col-md-4 rightBorder') 
    h3(class='title') Features
    div(class='content') 
     ul(class='features')
      li Unlimited Journals
      li Style your content
      li Multiple entries per day
      li Date and Time
      li Dropbox login 
   div(class='col-md-4 rightBorder')   
    h3(class='title') Security
    div(class='content') It is fully private. No one can see your journals. Digital Diary does not store your journals. Your journals will be storing in your dropbox.
   div(class='col-md-4')
    h3(class='title') Pricing
    div(class='content') It is absolutely free.
 
 div(class='modal fade' role='dialog' id='query')
  script(src='javascripts/home.js')
  div(class='modal-dialog')
   div(class='modal-content')
    div(class='modal-header')
     h3 Post your query. We will come back to you.
    div(class='modal-body')
     form(action='' method='' id='postQueryForm')
      input(type='name' class='form-control' name='name' placeholder='Name' required)
      br
      input(type='email' class='form-control' name='email' placeholder='Email' required)
      br
      textarea(name='query'  rows=7 class='form-control' placeholder='Write your query here ...' required)
      br
      div(class='text-center')
       button(type='submit' class='btn btn-primary') Post
